<div class="py-8 lg:py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl mb-6 leading-tight text-black dark:text-white font-black font-serif border-b-4 border-pink-500 pb-2 inline-block">
        Projects I've worked on
    </h1>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg md:text-3xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 italic font-serif">
        Over the years, I've enjoyed working with a wide range of clients, from small local businesses to large international companies.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:gap-8">
        <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="mb-4 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                The most rewarding work I've done has been within the Public Sector, where I've been able to make a measurable difference to people's lives, and the important jobs done by the people who serve them.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                I have also worked in the private sector, where I've helped businesses including Sainsbury's and npower to meet organisational goals by improving customer experience and increasing conversion rates.
            </p>
        </div>
        <figure class="w-3/5 sm:w-2/5 lg:w-2/5 mt-2 md:ml-4 md:mt-0 flex-shrink-0">
            <img src="/assets/images/workshop.jpeg"
                 class="rounded-lg shadow-md w-full"
                 alt="A photo of a workshop with the digital team at the Apprenticeship Service. The team are sat around a table, with a whiteboard behind them, a laptop and post-it notes are on the table."
                 width="800"
                 height="600">
            <figcaption class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">
                A workshop with the team at the Apprenticeship Service
            </figcaption>
        </figure>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-2 sm:mb-4 mt-12 font-semibold text-dark dark:text-white">Case studies</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 sm:mb-4 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        If you're interested in the type of work I've done, I've written up some short case studies.
    </p>
    <div class="space-y-6 md:space-y-8 divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-800 mb-8">
        {% for project in collections.project %}
            <div class="pt-6 md:pt-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
                    <a href="{{ project.url }}"
                       class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400">{{ project.data.title }}</a>
                </h3>
                {% if project.data.services %}
                    <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
                        {% for service in project.data.services %}
                            <li class="inline-flex px-1.5 md:px-2 py-0.5 md:py-1 text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded">
                                {{ service }}
                            </li>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </ul>
                {% endif %}
                <p class="text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">{{ project.data.description }}</p>
                <a href="{{ project.url }}"
                   class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-800 dark:hover:text-blue-300 underline">
                    Read case study
                    <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4"
                         fill="none"
                         viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                         stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</div>
